ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of JUDITH ANNE LAROCQUE of Hawkesbury, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of six months less a day; and designation of JUDITH ANNE LAROCQUE to be Vice-Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission on an interim basis, for a term of six months less a day, effective November 14, 2016.
